ive=\"polite\"\n      >\n        Built with{\" \"}\n        <a\n          className=\"underline hover:text-foreground\"\n          href=\"https://react-spectrum.adobe.com/react-aria/DateField.html\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n          rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\n        >\n          React Aria\n        </a>\n      </p>\n    </NumberField>\n  );\n}\n",
